{"tid":2293284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：不滿周庭「代言」兼「趕絕」華為  藍絲杯葛Donki 網民暗爽︰唔使逼（李八方）","createTime":"2020-11-20T06:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T11:53:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":125,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"82aeef37ed4b7b36d14665d8700007504ee59690","tid":2293284,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:40:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/6IP6VV67IZELLHZXNSOCJ563JU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F6IP6VV67IZELLHZXNSOCJ563JU%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=65f64e29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F6IP6VV67IZELLHZXNSOCJ563JU%2F&h=f84b2afc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/6IP6VV67IZELLHZXNSOCJ563JU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：不滿周庭「代言」兼「趕絕」華為 <br />\n藍絲杯葛Donki 網民暗爽︰唔使逼（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a8nNVOeRKQgC-uVJOibhOcOQBuI=/720x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JKDQL6KTUJGIVOXRQ7Z56YYMCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa8nNVOeRKQgC-uVJOibhOcOQBuI%3D%2F720x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJKDQL6KTUJGIVOXRQ7Z56YYMCU.jpg&h=afdd147a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周庭自行翻唱日本百貨公司Donki主題曲，藍絲揚言杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n近排藍絲成日出招，話要對付黃絲，不過藍絲盲目跟風向係常態，所以連打黃圈都會變為業餘，好似最近周庭喺YouTube翻唱日本百貨公司Donki（驚安之殿堂 ）主題曲，藍絲未搞清楚就號召杯葛Donki。但好多網民暗爽，話少啲人去唔使咁逼！<br />\n<br />\n日前周庭喺YouTube上載咗翻唱Don Don Donki驚安之殿堂嘅日文同廣東話主題曲，仲去咗Donki取景拍自製MV，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J-MdvMRdgwYlDpZhJVOPhJbnxrM=/963x664/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MOEHAS3O3BF3DKG2MMMB4S5HXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ-MdvMRdgwYlDpZhJVOPhJbnxrM%3D%2F963x664%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMOEHAS3O3BF3DKG2MMMB4S5HXU.jpg&h=0a06f832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■藍絲群組話華為手機下載唔到Donki App，結果又話杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KFkHp8gNgmz1S4dEhyF-GftjEh4=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GLQI5OJIQBEYVFKHPJC56CMBCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKFkHp8gNgmz1S4dEhyF-GftjEh4%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGLQI5OJIQBEYVFKHPJC56CMBCI.jpg&h=6bef9f31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■上月Donki中環分店開幕，大批市民朝聖。<br />\n冇晒中國客 日本盈利照創新高<br />\n<br />\n最近藍絲又有人發帖，話華為手機下載唔到Donki App，結果又話杯葛，有網民解釋，話華為手機冇Google Play，咁點下載呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實不論周庭唱Donki主題曲定冇得下載Donki App，藍絲硬要老屈Donki，堅持抵制、直至道歉為止。但Donki其實唔使靠中國市場同中國遊客，母公司剛公佈業績，日本冇晒中國客，Donki嘅盈利都創新高，有網民仲叫藍絲找數，一定要杯葛Donki ，少啲人去唔使咁逼！<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"44da966d252517f9a2d80db962c02bc208f833ea","tid":2293284,"uid":103230,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:41:35.000Z","msg":"原來有呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美心有冇歌架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d21e426a177eca8cc7eecf3ef44f7d672b9ada6","tid":2293284,"uid":47202,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:43:42.000Z","msg":"叫Gphone自己拍番個富臨廣告啦"},{"pid":"b5db51606972f04a48370560f8ab0f2fd9e4dfb6","tid":2293284,"uid":85586,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:44:36.000Z","msg":"藍絲一係無錢買一係貪平<br />\n搞個優惠咪又狗衝去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a711344bf522e5335f9208dabb7866e89c0263","tid":22